# ====== Electron 构建相关配置 ======
# electron 和构建工具使用阿里云镜像
electron:registry=https://registry.npmmirror.com/
electron-builder:registry=https://registry.npmmirror.com/

# electron 下载源配置
# 使用 npmmirror 的 mirrors 路径（包含 v{version} 目录结构），避免某些版本在 raw 路径上 404
# Note: setting plain ENV-style entries in .npmrc (like "ELECTRON_MIRROR=...")
# causes "Unknown env config" warnings on newer npm versions. Prefer setting
# these as real environment variables in CI or your shell, or keep defaults in
# build scripts (see scripts/build.js). Example (bash):
#   export ELECTRON_MIRROR=https://npmmirror.com/mirrors/electron/
#   export ELECTRON_BUILDER_BINARIES_MIRROR=https://npmmirror.com/mirrors/electron-builder-binaries/

